Commands:
npx create-react-app my-app
cd my-app
npm start

npm run build
(yarn build)
npm serve download 
npm i -g serve (basic http server)
serve -s build -p 8000 (build folder) run in production server the production build folder

fake backend jsonserv
npm i json-server

    in package.json -> "server": "json-server --watch db.json --port 5000"

npm run server 


router is not included by default we need to install package for that
npm i react-router-dom

download bootstrap
npm i bootstrap@4.1.1

 